  **PART 2 --- RESIDENTIAL CONSTRUCTION CODES**

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------

Applies to: One- and two-family dwellings, townhouses up to 3 stories,
and accessory structures. Residential projects in Utah are primarily
governed by the International Residential Code (IRC) with Utah-specific
amendments.

