  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **⚠ UTAH ADOPTION NOTE:** Salt Lake City and the Wasatch Front are in a
  HIGH seismic hazard zone due to the Wasatch Fault. Most commercial and
  industrial buildings in the SLC area fall in Seismic Design Category D.
  A licensed geotechnical engineer\'s report (geotech report) is required
  for most commercial and industrial projects. Liquefaction potential is
  a significant concern in many SLC valley soils.

